snippet.title: Modern Warfare 2 Prestige Edition Unboxing (Official)
snippet.description: The first official look at the Prestige Collectors Edition of Modern Warfare 2 - available for pre-order now and releasing worldwide on November 10th, 2009. MW2 on Twitter - follow @fourzerotwo
